title: Call of Duty 4 Modern Warfare
description:
================================
Call of Duty 4 - Modern Warfare
================================
The game does not need a installation...
1. Just run the file called "makeDesktopIcon"

Now you can play and have much fun

============
Multiplayer
============
To play multiplayer, you got to follow theese steps:
1. Start CoD4 Multiplayer (You will get an error from PunkBuster, ignore it)
2. Go to Options -> Multiplayer Options -> Enter Key Code (You will find the key codes in the bottom of the ReadMe file)
3. (This depends on your keyboard) Open the console. Do this by pressing ~ (English keyboard)
[If you have another keyboard, press the button right under Esc]
4. Now, type: connect [IP]:[Port] An example: connect 195.1.30.117:28960
5. Now you are ready to play mutliplayer. (Some problems may come the first times you play, about 1-6 times: PunkBuster will kick
you for different reasons. This will stop after you have been playing some times online)
6. Remember, you can only play on cracked servers, to find them, go here:


For more info, read the ReadMe file
